Form Element - Single Line Text Input - cml:text

- Renders a single line text field
- Accepts all Common Attributes

[code] <cml:text label="Sample text field:" /> [/code]

<img src="sample_text_field.png" />

Additional attributes

[code] default [/code]
If supplied, the value of this attribute will be pre-filled in the text box when the page is loaded. It will not be submitted and will fail the [code]required[/code] validator until the contributor enters text into it.

[code] <cml:text label="Sample text field:" default="Enter text here" /> [/code]

<img src="sample_text_field_with_default.png" />